<br>
==Annotations==
025.21 '''beldam's''' {{spaces|5}} an archaic word meaning "hag" or "witch", may also refer to an old woman, particularly an ugly one.<ref>[[http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Beldam Wikipedia entry Beldam]]</ref>


