<br>
==Annotations==
'''Herring's blush'''{{spaces|5}}(''proverbial'') ''It would make a red herring blush'' is used proverbially to describe something very shameful. Bloom, however, is misusing the phrase to describe Davy Byrne's rosy cheeks.


