==Annotations==
'''''Que voulez-vous?'' Moore would say'''{{spaces|5}}(''French'') ''“What do you expect?” Moore would say''.<ref>Gifford (1988) 247-248.</ref> The Irish writer and critic [[w:George Moore (novelist)|George Moore]] was fond of embellishing his conversation with French phrases, a habit he developed during the seven years he spent studying art in Paris.

