'''''basso profondo'''''{{spaces|5}}(''Italian'') a very deep bass voice.<ref>Gifford (1988) 278.</ref> ''[[wikt:basso profondo|Basso profondo]]'' is a [[w:Glossary of musical terminology|musical term]].

