==Annotations==
'''''Bi i dho husht'''''{{spaces|5}}(''Irish'') ''Be quiet''. The correct Irish form is: ''[[wikt:tost#Irish|Bí i do thost]]''. The final word is pronounced [hɔsˠt̪ˠ] (approximately: ''hawst''). The Citizen has clearly confused this with the unrelated English word ''hush'', which implies that he is by no means a fluent speaker of his native tongue.

